data.description: HUGE PRICE DROP ALERT! Beautiful Southwestern Style Ranch Home on nearly a 3/4 acre lot! The front has a custom brick circular driveway for great curb appeal. This beautiful home has a huge open floorplan with 3,271 square feet of living space. Huge Master (primary) bedroom suite with 2 additional master bedrooms. That is 3 Master Bedrooms! Beautiful Saltillo Tile Flooring highlights the home along with high beamed ceilings. Kitchen is to die for with a huge tiled island along with plenty of cabinet space. The property has a nice gameroom or covered patio area along with plenty of outside space to park your RV, boat, toys, and even raise your favorite farm animals. There are several outer buildings which give you plenty of space to store your tools and toys. You must see this beautiful home to appreciate all it has to offer. This property has the perfect pool-sized lot and plenty of room to add on or convert the garage to an ADU unit. This home is in a quiet neighborhood that is close to shopping, grocery, schools, parks and worship.
